data.description: Discover this charming 4-bed, 2-bath home on nearly 3/4 of an acre in a great location. With hardwood floors on the main level and the privacy of a fenced backyard, this home is perfect for entertaining or unwinding in tranquility. With spacious interiors, this residence offers a seamless blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the chance to make this property your own, providing a perfect retreat within reach of all amenities.    NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
